Ozzie is a series of children's educational games. They all star Ozzie S. Otter (voiced by Haley Joel Osment), a curious and imaginative young 7-year-old orphaned sea otter pup who serves as the series' main protagonist. The games focus on teaching children science and ecology in different environments. They also include several activities, stories, mini games and experiments to try out. The software titles were also released in the French language by Emme Interactive.
